An implementation of the model object 'SCorpus Graph'.

The following features are implemented:

  • SDocuments
  • Salt Project
  • SCorpora
  • SCorpus Relations
  • SCorpus Document Relations

getSCorpus

public SCorpus getSCorpus(de.hu_berlin.german.korpling.saltnpepper.salt.saltCore.SElementId sCorpusId)
Returns an SCorpus element corresponding to sCorpusId. If non exists, null will be returned. Null will also be returned, if sCorpusId is null or the id belongs to a SNode-object, which is not of type SCorpus.

addSSubCorpus

public de.hu_berlin.german.korpling.saltnpepper.salt.saltCore.SElementId addSSubCorpus(SCorpus sSuperCorpus,
                                                                                       SCorpus sSubCorpus)
Adds the given sSubCorpus to the SCorpusGraph object and creates an SCorpusRelation between the given sSuperCorpus and the sSubCorpus, if and only if the sSuperCorpus is already added to this object. Otherwise an exception will be thrown. The method returns the SElementId for the generated SCorpusRelation object.

Specified by:
addSSubCorpus in interface SCorpusGraph
Parameters:
sSuperCorpus - corpus which already has to be added
sSubCorpus - corpus to add
Returns:
the SElementId for the generated SCorpusRelation object.
